citations:
    citation-adwd-daenerys-i:
        source: source-adwd
        properties:
            locator: "Daenerys I"
            accessed: "2026-03-06"
        notes: "POV: Daenerys Targaryen. Daenerys is ruling Meereen. She is dealing with petitioners, including freedmen complaining about the guilds and slavers seeking to reopen the fighting pits. She refuses to reopen the pits. Hizdahr zo Loraq is introduced as a suitor urging her to reopen the pits. The Shavepate (Skahaz mo Kandaq) and Reznak mo Reznak serve as her advisors. Her dragons Rhaegal and Viserion are chained in the pit; Drogon has flown away."
